a thorough coverage of this genre 'lowbrow art ' blends pop culture , street culture , pop art and surrealism with a strong focus on controversial sub-cultures from bikers to 60s sitcoms . it 's about time that a thorough coverage of this genre is presented , and painter and journalist matt dukes jordan provides a spirited assessment of the high points of lowbrow in weirdo deluxe : the wild world of pop surrealism & lowbrow art . full-page color reproductions of such art , from labels to paintings , present both art displays and commentary on the artists creating them .